{"type":"text","timestamp":1781081451493,"sessionID":"ses_14f476edcffe1MiVLPNn4U9ix4","part":{"id":"prt_eb0ba1af0001C3j1U8LuBoCyWH","messageID":"msg_eb0ba0fe6001lQGVPaSw18hM60","sessionID":"ses_14f476edcffe1MiVLPNn4U9ix4","type":"text","text":"Reward design audit complete: **PASS**.\n\n- **Formula**: single-tier weighted sum — `score = 1.0 × (cases_passed / 5)` over 5 binary byte-exact diff checks against GNU ls on a 10k-entry directory, each with 60s per-case timeout.\n- **All 6 checks pass**: correctness gated by exact diff, implementation-agnostic (only output matters), no gameable dimension imbalance (5 binary cases), shortcuts blocked (execve tripwire + sha256 identity check + banned-crate grep + build-from-source enforcement), scoring is modular (standalone `compute_reward.py` with `python3 -ISs`, no agent imports), and both success/failure paths emit valid `reward.json` with required schema.\n- **No notes/fixes needed.**\n\nOutput written to `results/pre-qa/reward_design.json`.","time":{"start":1781081447152,"end":1781081451488}}}
